public abstract class DEActor
extends ptolemy.actor.TypedAtomicActor
implements SequenceActor, ptolemy.actor.TimedActor
The base class for actors specific to the DE domain. This class implements both SequenceActor and TimedActor.

A DE domain-specific actor, like the TimedDelay actor, needs to extend this class. However, it does not mean only actors extending this class can be used in the DE domain. For example, the Clock actor can be used in DE domain.

    • DEActor

      protected DEActor​(ptolemy.kernel.CompositeEntity container, java.lang.String name) throws ptolemy.kernel.util.NameDuplicationException, ptolemy.kernel.util.IllegalActionException
      Construct an actor with the specified container and name. This is protected because there is no reason to create an instance of this class, but derived classes will want to invoke the constructor of the superclass.
      Parameters:
      container - The container.
      name - The name.
      Throws:
      ptolemy.kernel.util.IllegalActionException - If the entity cannot be contained by the proposed container.
      ptolemy.kernel.util.NameDuplicationException - If the container already has an actor with this name.
